@model IEnumerable<FinalProjectMVC.ViewModels.Blog.BlogPostVM>

<body>
    <div class="container-main">
        <div class="headof">
            <h1>BLOG POST PAGE</h1>
            <div class="nav1">
                <a href="#">Home</a> &gt; <a href="#">Blog</a> &gt; Blog with Left Sidebar
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="sidebar">
                
               
          
                <div class="sidebar-section">
                    <h3>DETAIL RESERVATION</h3>
                    <div class="reservation-detail">
                        <h4>PICKING UP LOCATION</h4>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> 15 January 2015 / 08:00 am<br><i class="fa fa-plane"></i> From SkyLine AirPort</p>
                        <h4>DROPPING OFF LOCATION</h4>
                        <p><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i> 15 January 2015 / 08:00 am<br><i class="fa fa-plane"></i> From SkyLine AirPort</p>
                        <button class="btn">UPDATE RESERVATION</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="sidebar-section">
                    <h3>TESTIMONIALS</h3>
                    <div class="testimonials">
                        <p>Vivamus eget nibh. Etiam cursus leo vel metus. Nulla facilisi. Aenean nec eros. Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia.</p>
                        <p>John Doe<br>Co-founder at Rent It</p>
                        <div class="testimonial-dots">
                            <span class="dot active"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                            <span class="dot"></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
              

                <div class="sidebar-section">
                    <h3>TWITTER</h3>
                    <div class="twitter-feed">
                        <div class="tweet">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
                            <span class="twitter-handle">twittername</span> At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores et ea rebum. Stet clita kasd gubergren, no sea takimata sanctus est Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
                            <div class="tweet-time">1 minute ago</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="tweet">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
                            <span class="twitter-handle">twittername</span> At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores et ea rebum. Stet clita kasd gubergren, no sea takimata sanctus est Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.
                            <div class="tweet-time">1 minute ago</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
            </div>
            <main class="main-content">

                <div class="post">
                <div class="container mt-5">

                    @if (Model != null && Model.Any())
                    {
                        @foreach (var post in Model)
                        {
                            <div class="post mb-5">
                                <div class="post-image">
                                    <img src="@post.ImageUrl" alt="@post.Title" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
                                </div>
                                <div class="post-content mt-3">
                                    <h1 class="post-title">@post.Title</h1>
                                    <p class="post-meta">
                                        By @post.Author / @post.CreatedAt.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")
                                    </p>
                                    <p class="post-text">
                                        @post.Content.Substring(0, Math.Min(post.Content.Length, 200))...
                                    </p>
                                    <a href="@Url.Action("Details", "Blog", new { id = post.Id })" class="btn btn-primary">READ MORE</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        }
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <p class="text-center text-muted">No blog posts available at the moment.</p>
                    }
                </div>
                </div>



                <div class="post">
                <div class="quote-section">
                    <blockquote>
                        Fusce gravida interdum eros a mollis. Sed non lorem varius, volutpat nisl in, laoreet ante. Quisque suscipit mauris ipsum, eu mollis arcu laoreet vel.
                    </blockquote>
                    <cite>— ISA MERCAN</cite>
                </div>
                <p class="post-meta">By author name here / 6th June 2014 / in Design, Photography / 27 Comments / 18 Likes / Share This Post</p>
                <button class="read-more">READ MORE</button>
            </div>

            </main>


    
</body>
